  "content": {
    "prompt": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following best helps to explain why <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"N a, solid\"><math alttext=\"N a, solid\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Na</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is more reactive with water than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"M g, solid\"><math alttext=\"M g, solid\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Mg</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is?</p>\n",
